<div class="row m-5">
  <div class="col text-center">
    <div class="h1">Simplify Your Song Tabs Management</div>
    <div>Music Tab is here to revolutionize the way you manage your song tabs</div>
    <% if !user_signed_in? %>
      <div>
        <%= link_to "Get Started", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-info m-5 px-5 py-3", aria: { label: "Get Started" } %>
      </div>

      <div>
        <%= link_to "Sign-in", new_user_session_path, class: "btn btn-sm btn-outline-info", aria: { current: "page" } %>
      </div>
    <% else %>
      <img src="<%= asset_path 'music_notes.png' %>" alt="Notes Tabs" class="small-image m-4">
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="h4 text-center mt-4">Why Choose Music Tab?</div>
<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
  <div class="row m-5 w-75 text-center">
    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="list-group" id="list-tab" role="tablist">
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active" id="list-1-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-1" role="tab" aria-controls="list-1">Effortless Tab Management</a>
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="list-2-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-2" role="tab" aria-controls="list-2">Intuitive Interface</a>
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="list-3-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-3" role="tab" aria-controls="list-3">Stay Organized</a>
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="list-4-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-4" role="tab" aria-controls="list-4">Enhance Your Productivity</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-8 d-flex align-items-center">
      <div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="list-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-1-list">Say goodbye to the hassle of paper tabs. With Music Tab, you can easily create, organize, and access your song tabs in a centralized digital format.</div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-2-list">Designed with musicians in mind, our user-friendly interface makes managing your tabs a breeze. Spend less time searching and more time playing.</div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-3-list">Never lose a tab again. Keep all your songs neatly organized in one place, ensuring you always have accurate and cohesive records at your fingertips.</div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-4" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-4-list">Update and edit your tabs effortlessly. Focus on your music without the distraction of disorganized notes.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="h4 text-center m-4">How to navigate Music Tab</div>
<div class="container d-flex justify-content-center">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div class="col-8 d-flex align-items-center">
      <div class="tab-content" id="nav-tabContent">
        <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="list-index" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-index-list">The list view shows all tabs with titles. Users can click on a tab to view or edit it. A plus (+) button allows adding new tabs.<br>
          <img src="<%= asset_path 'index.jpeg' %>" alt="All Tabs" class="big-image">
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-create" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-create-list">Users can create a new tab by entering a title and content. The content field supports rich text formatting and file attachments. Click "Submit" to save.
          <img src="<%= asset_path 'create.jpeg' %>" alt="Create Tabs" class="big-image">
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-show" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-show-list">Users can view the full content of a created tab. The tab displays all the formatted details entered during creation or editing, allowing for easy reference during practice or performance.
          <img src="<%= asset_path 'show.jpeg' %>" alt="View Tabs" class="big-image">
        </div>
        <div class="tab-pane fade" id="list-edit" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="list-edit-list">Users can edit the title and content of an existing tab with rich text options. Save changes after editing.
          <img src="<%= asset_path 'edit.jpeg' %>" alt="Edit Tabs" class="big-image">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="list-group" id="list-tab" role="tablist">
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action active" id="list-index-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-index" role="tab" aria-controls="list-index">View All Tabs</a>
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="list-create-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-create" role="tab" aria-controls="list-create">Create a Tab</a>
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="list-show-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-show" role="tab" aria-controls="list-show">View Tab</a>
        <a class="list-group-item list-group-item-action" id="list-edit-list" data-bs-toggle="list" href="#list-edit" role="tab" aria-controls="list-edit">Edit Tab</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

